00:41:45.260 --> 00:41:46.260
thoughts and tips.

00:41:46.260 --> 00:41:48.260
And no doubt, it's not an exhaustive list.

00:41:48.260 --> 00:41:50.780
There's other things that we could add to it.

00:41:50.780 --> 00:41:58.980
Lord, ultimately, our desire, my desire is that we would glorify thee.

00:41:58.980 --> 00:42:04.960
To summarize it as John the Baptist said, I must decrease.

00:42:04.960 --> 00:42:06.420
You must increase.

00:42:06.420 --> 00:42:13.500
Lord, help us to live our lives in such a way that you would be honored and glorified.

00:42:13.500 --> 00:42:14.760
Work in hearts and lives.

00:42:14.760 --> 00:42:18.880
Maybe there's some things that some folks need to incorporate in their lives, some decisions

00:42:18.880 --> 00:42:24.060
that they need to make this evening as they evaluate the previous year and look forward

00:42:24.060 --> 00:42:25.500
to a new year.

00:42:25.500 --> 00:42:29.840
Not being presumptuous, but simply planning, trying to be good stewards.

00:42:29.840 --> 00:42:35.680
Or would you help us to be responsive?

00:42:35.680 --> 00:42:36.680
Help us to be obedient.

00:42:36.680 --> 00:42:38.120
Well, thank you for every decision.

00:42:38.120 --> 00:42:39.240
For it's in Christ's name we pray.

00:42:39.240 --> 00:42:40.240
Would you stand with me?

00:42:40.240 --> 00:42:40.240


